name: Welcome to my website
body: ### Welcome to GitHub Pages. https://media.licdn.com/media/AAEAAQAAAAAAAASEAAAAJDIyYjg0ZDY1LTUzZTAtNDllYi04NTU2LTUzYzI5ZTY2N2U5NA.jpg I'm a Masters in Computer Information Systems from Boston University. I am a Data Analytics/Science enthusiast. While pursuing my Masters, during the summer break of 2015 I enrolled in the Udacity's Data Analyst Nanodegree MOOC. I interacted with similar enthusiasts from across the globe through udacity's blog and worked on several Analytics projects as well as helped others overcome their obstacles analyzing data.
